OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779825947
OL,3,CFire breaks out at home in Leicester
OL,4,Cafter e-bike left on charge
OL,6,FOne person has been treated for burns
OL,7,Fand smoke inhalation after a fire
OL,8,Fcaused by an e-bike broke out at a
OL,9,Fhome in Leicester.
OL,11,FLeicestershire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,12,F(LFRS) were called to Westleigh Road
OL,13,Fat around 4.30am on Monday (25 May).
OL,15,FEmergency crews spent more than ten
OL,16,Fhours at the scene, with the incident
OL,17,Fnot concluded until just after 3pm.
OL,19,FIn a statement, LFRS said the cause of
OL,20,Fthe fire was believed to have been an
OL,21,Fe-bike left on charge.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
