OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779825947
OL,3,CFire breaks out at home in Leicester
OL,4,Cafter e-bike left on charge
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "We attended a
OL,7,Ffire on 25 May at a 3-storey property
OL,8,Fon Westleigh Road at 04:31.
OL,10,F"During the incident we requested a
OL,11,Fmake pumps five. Time of stop was
OL,12,F15:04. All persons were accounted for.
OL,13,FOne casualty was treated for burns and
OL,14,Fsmoke inhalation and left in the care
OL,15,Fof EMAS. The cause is believed to have
OL,16,Fbeen an e-bike on charge."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
