PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779825947
OL,3,CFire breaks out at home in Leicester
OL,4,Cafter e-bike left on charge
OL,6,FFollowing the blaze, LFRS issued a
OL,7,Fwarning about the risks of lithium-ion
OL,8,Fbatteries used in e-bikes and e-
OL,9,Fscooters, saying they "can become
OL,10,Fextremely dangerous if damaged,
OL,11,Fovercharged, or used with the wrong
OL,12,Fcharger".
OL,14,FThe service advised owners to always
OL,15,Fuse the correct charger, never charge
OL,16,Fovernight or near exits, avoid
OL,17,Fblocking hallways and doorways, and to
OL,18,Fstop using damaged batteries
OL,19,Fimmediately.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
