PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779825947
OL,3,CFire breaks out at home in Leicester
OL,4,Cafter e-bike left on charge
OL,6,FPhotographs from inside the property
OL,7,Fhave been released by LFRS, where a
OL,8,Fclosed internal door between a
OL,9,Fcorridor and the kitchen acted as a
OL,10,Fbarrier to the flames.
OL,12,FA spokesperson said closing internal
OL,13,Fdoors at night or when leaving the
OL,14,Fhouse can slow the spread of fire and
OL,15,Fsmoke, protect escape routes and give
OL,16,Fresidents vital extra time to escape
OL,17,Fsafely.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
